クラス DefaultContextDataFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.astamuse.asta4d.data.DefaultContextDataFinder
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    ContextDataFinder

    public class DefaultContextDataFinder
extends Object
implements ContextDataFinder
    A default implementation of ContextDataFinder. It will search data in a given order (if scope is not specified) and try to apply predefined ContextDataFinder list to convert data to appropriate type.
    作成者:
    e-ryu
